<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朋友们，我们的公主现在全心全意地爱着这片湖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道最好的跳水地点在哪里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道最高的河岸在哪里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还知道各种鱼和动物都生活在哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，艾伦马上就感觉到了湖在变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她第一次有感觉是在和王子一起游泳的时候。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她快速浮出水面，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看了看四周：“湖有问题！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子也跟着她浮出水面：“没什么问题呀。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！湖不一样了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦开始向湖的更深处游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子跟在她身后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想知道她是不是病了：“艾伦，你没事吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦没有回答他，也没有回头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从一个地方游到另一个地方，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仔细检查着这片湖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天他们见面时，艾伦非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“湖岸太干了，草和植物都快死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦指着岩石，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看那些岩石！它们以前是在水下的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>困惑的王子想要安慰她，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是被艾伦推开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太可怕了！”艾伦喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“湖水正在流失！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝在洞穴里待了七天七夜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，水龙掉到了地上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它很快就干了，又变回了海草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝捡起海草，她抬起头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发现水开始从石头上滴下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咒语起作用了！”她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖水很快就会涌入洞穴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她必须回到楼上……要快！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，艾格尼丝来到湖边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖里几乎已经没有水了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但湖底还有一些浅浅的水坑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝皱起眉头：“咒语花的时间太长了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，艾格尼丝又回到湖边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>给每个地方都洒了魔法药水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她又去了王宫和公主的窗前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，王国里的河流都停止了流动，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有水再从山上流下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喷泉和水井都干了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就连婴儿的眼泪也干了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 终于，湖里最后的一点儿水也消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>